  15 Feb 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org> +xerces-1.4.4.ebuild:
  Added a version bump to 1.4.4 in the 1.3 slot. Can't be committed to main
  until reverse dependency atoms are fixed.

  12 Jan 2007; Vlastimil Babka <caster@gentoo.org> +xerces-2.9.0.ebuild,
  +files/xerces-2.9.0-gentoo.patch, +files/xerces-2.9.0-no_dom3.patch:
  Version bump, bug #156258. Now using xalan-serializer for DOM Level 3
  serialization as upstream recommends.

